name: nutmegmix
description:
An NAI/anything based recipe with SD, smirking face (nsfw SD), r34 concepts, and another model i forgot about inside.

Recipe is from an anonymous user. I'm just uploading it here for convenience since i'm using this model a lot for sampling my loras or testing the community's creations.
The fact it incorporate SD and smirking face allow the model to (sometimes...) understand the part of the prompts which are written in natural langage instead of being forced to only using gelbooru tags.

It have a tendency to fuck ups the eyes and the mouth of the subject sometimes. You can play around with your face restoration settings or use a lora artstyle to prevent that.
